cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Colette Corpus — Therapeutic Patient Education for Liver Transplant Recipients"
abstract: >-
  Information and therapeutic patient education (TPE) corpus for liver
  transplant patients: clinical factsheets and a reference question-and-answer
  database, developed and validated by the healthcare team at the Henri Bismuth
  Hepato-Biliary Center (Paul-Brousse Hospital, AP-HP).
type: dataset
message: >-
  If you reuse this corpus, please cite it (see the 'How to cite' section
  in the README). The citation applies to the dataset, distributed under the
  CC-BY-SA 4.0 license.
